Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.04,0:15:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  嗯\N开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.60,0:15:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好性感喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.92,0:15:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都穿这样好了  每天吗\N适合你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.84,0:15:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有看过自己的样子吗\N有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.19,0:16:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常适合你\N内裤也快看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.96,0:16:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有胸罩吗  没有\N真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.20,0:16:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看一下  过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.48,0:16:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超性感的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.92,0:16:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辣妹喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.28,0:16:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带着眼镜也很性感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.04,0:17:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好性感的打扮喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.40,0:17:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经算成功一半了\N真的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.40,0:17:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是家教老师吧   是的\N主要教什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.48,0:17:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是辣妹家教\N要教口交
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.28,0:18:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辣妹老师  超M的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.32,0:18:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好诱人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.52,0:18:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石着摄影机喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.12,0:18:41.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说什么呢\N盯着看五秒钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.36,0:18:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就可以了\N服务一下大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.52,0:19:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引诱一下大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.12,0:19:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在学生面前喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.00,0:19:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问学生想怎么样呢\N怎么硬了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.96,0:19:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到老师那么兴奋啊\N你想干什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.20,0:19:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吧\N要学起来喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.52,0:19:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吧  有点难耶\N因为没做过吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.48,0:19:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先练习一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.16,0:20:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把我当学生练习吧\N来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.64,0:20:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是学生\N虽然是三十年前的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.72,0:20:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,练习看看吧\N贵志同学喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.80,0:20:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴奋吗\N贵志怎么变那么大呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.24,0:20:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是老师害的吗\N有那么兴奋吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.60,0:21:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不可以喔\N要像这样子说不行喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.40,0:21:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  还不让你射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.00,0:21:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续\N你想怎么样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.56,0:21:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.60,0:21:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用手让我爽  爽吗\N爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.84,0:21:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师我快射了\N都还没直接摸耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.12,0:22:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要我摸吧\N蛮喜欢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.52,0:22:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要忍耐喔\N怎么办呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.56,0:22:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说可以呢  不用忍耐没关系喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.00,0:22:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.92,0:22:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒  太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.20,0:22:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着镜头喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.32,0:22:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.16,0:22:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.88,0:23:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那里呢\N要假装一下下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.04,0:23:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在看那里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.00,0:23:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.64,0:23:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵志想爽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.60,0:24:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮你脱内裤吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.84,0:24:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变大了喔\N怎么办呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.88,0:24:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好硬喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.48,0:24:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:03.16,0:25:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:07.96,0:26:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在抽动喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:17.40,0:26:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:19.32,0:27:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁股如何呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:55.00,0:27:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龟头如何呢
