Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:53.40,0:28:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:05.88,0:31:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要射吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:12.11,0:31:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师帮你喔\N想要射在那里呢  嘴巴吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:28.28,0:31:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮你吹出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:46.84,0:31:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:00.28,0:32:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢一点  受不了了\N可以射吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:43.64,0:32:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射在嘴里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:03.48,0:33:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:13.56,0:33:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滴下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:13.72,0:33:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滴下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:26.36,0:33:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有像这样射那么多的学生吧\N好爽喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:37.56,0:33:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射在嘴里真爽啊
