Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:31.96,0:35:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要做什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:45.56,0:35:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专心\N不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:48.76,0:35:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好念书喔\N无法专心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:59.00,0:36:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先念这本吧\N好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:14.68,0:36:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师好想被你摸喔\N你在说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:21.08,0:36:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不小心说出口了\N对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:24.12,0:36:32.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好念书才行\N今天念日本史喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:48.92,0:36:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始咯   好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:57.40,0:37:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里开始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:03.64,0:37:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有在听吗  有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:11.16,0:37:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师的内裤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:17.56,0:37:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师的内裤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:21.40,0:37:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放在高府里的是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:27.64,0:37:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师的内裤  有在听吗\N我说仕么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:41.88,0:37:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不专心老师要生气了\N我很认真啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:48.76,0:37:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高府吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:56.92,0:38:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前有人在里面藏了什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:06.20,0:38:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗大便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:10.68,0:38:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦\N但应该有狗大便啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:15.96,0:38:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想应该是有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:18.36,0:38:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案是填轮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:25.40,0:38:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要写汉字喔\N那有汉字啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:33.40,0:38:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是埴轮  懂吗\N那写写看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:48.12,0:38:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在念的懂吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:03.00,0:39:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道  是吗\N我忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:10.36,0:39:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内裤\N不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:12.76,0:39:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么呢\N答案是古坟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:21.56,0:39:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写写看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:30.04,0:39:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用汉字写啦\N有汉字吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:42.52,0:39:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:52.12,0:39:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:57.24,0:40:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办呢\N想看内裤  你刚胸部又碰到我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:07.64,0:40:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师\N怎么样  不喜欢吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:13.40,0:40:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很害羞啊\N贵志真可爱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:22.20,0:40:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这样子上课如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:28.76,0:40:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师胸部好软喔\N老师的胸部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:39.32,0:40:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有在听吗\N你说什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:43.80,0:40:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冈山县冈山市最大的古境是什么\N浦山古坟   你怎么知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:53.88,0:40:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正确耶\N因为你胸部顶着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:00.12,0:41:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思啦\N老师可是很正经的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:07.80,0:41:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师休息一下吧\N也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:16.60,0:41:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师  有个请求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:21.24,0:41:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  我穿这样怪怪的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:26.20,0:41:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是没问题\N但有个请求希望你能听听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:32.60,0:41:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老市穿这样很害羞耶\N可以听我的请求吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:40.92,0:41:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呢  起立一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:51.32,0:41:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:00.60,0:42:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:07.48,0:42:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要看内裤  老师拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:18.20,0:42:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要摸摸看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:24.76,0:42:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跨到我上面来   好棒的内裤\N那里买的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:36.12,0:42:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跨上去吗   对的\N拜托老师
